{"tid":682582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女上司 vs 男上司","createTime":"2018-05-29T03:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T05:15:50.000Z","uid":75655,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6c2f7f67a61fcd4acb4b70ecda0694997d450b","tid":682582,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"小弟做野幾年既觀察-<br />\n<br />\n女上司既所謂management 就只不過係一部人肉cctv 乜撚都督住晒 好似追數咁 恨不得捉住啲下屬對手去做啲daily routine野 有森林唔睇就去睇樹葉有無生蟲<br />\n<br />\n相反男上事好多時會放手比下屬發揮 唔會當下屬係小朋友咁督住晒 真係會去研究下成個制度有無不足 去改善成個工作流程<br />\n<br />\n結論係 你班女人都係返屋企同老公含撚同湊仔啦！<br />\n<br />\nreference<br />\n女上司 vs 男上司<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/559420/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/559420/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4965478c844632ced1a3d7047aa065999ba04ceb","tid":682582,"uid":99024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:49:01.000Z","msg":"男上司for sure"},{"pid":"df57c683e860711a6353d159921508e66440d9f0","tid":682582,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea8da654c9cb6c04ac9a6379b644166d933e540","tid":682582,"uid":48993,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:56:16.000Z","msg":"女上司每日脾氣一覽表：<br />\n<br />\nm到前<br />\nm到前<br />\nm到<br />\nm到<br />\nm到<br />\nm到<br />\nm到<br />\nm到後<br />\n心情好可能讚吓你（僅限佢鐘意嘅同事）<br />\n鬧人<br />\n扮關心你<br />\n鬧人<br />\n扮關心你"},{"pid":"78e61b04ae297aee23fbf47fd1076c3ff8f183dc","tid":682582,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T03:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse